{"tid":2424243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好撚鍾意霍格華茲啊","createTime":"2021-02-26T12:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T14:09:35.000Z","uid":234428,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41a9285e21f19368bac48757550cc01ccca12567","tid":2424243,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:10:13.000Z","msg":"妙麗：走啦哈利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />離開霍格華茲先有機會對抗佛地魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哈利波特：唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要同霍格華茲共存亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n妙麗：依家嘅霍格華茲 已經唔係我哋鍾意嘅霍格華茲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家只係極權嘅一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔走 保護好自己 如果連你都犧牲埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁到時邊個拯救霍格華茲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哈利波特：唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係懦夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n榮恩：<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走啦哈利 人冇事先可以做世界冠軍啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef0ef2d2f1018a61591bfe6f40bae495df26937","tid":2424243,"uid":92299,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:12:44.000Z","msg":"食霍格華茲canteen對抗佛地魔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc435d7f1fd8a34ab6ee346ddac0e37c250dfecd","tid":2424243,"uid":39263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:14:15.000Z","msg":"睇小説勿認真"},{"pid":"fc14d6263466a3511ff1427516d74cea6999b49e","tid":2424243,"uid":234428,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:16:30.000Z","msg":"講咗d 咩 自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif